<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.95.98384.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Phylogram of Tubakiaceae based on combined ITS, LSU, tef 1 and tub 2 loci. Numbers above the branches indicate maximum parsimony bootstrap (MP BP ≥ 50 %), ML bootstrap values (ML-BS ≥ 50 %) and Bayesian Posterior Probabilities (BPP ≥ 0.9). The tree is rooted with Melanconis groenlandica (CBS 116540). Ex-type strains are marked with *, and strains from the present study are marked in bold blue." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/793188" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

